<div id="review_1808447288" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1808447288" />
    <a title="Filipa" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4459767-filipa"><img alt="Filipa" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1579788330p2/4459767.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1808447288?book_show_action=true">Jun 13, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Filipa" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Filipa" href="/user/show/4459767-filipa">Filipa</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title=" 9780701178994" href="/book/show/899211.Skylight_Confessions">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4459767-filipa?shelf=english-books">english-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4459767-filipa?shelf=not-own">not-own</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4459767-filipa?shelf=borrowed">borrowed</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4459767-filipa?shelf=2018-reads">2018-reads</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4459767-filipa?shelf=magical-realism">magical-realism</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4459767-filipa?shelf=mental-health">mental-health</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1808447288" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4298338191782475205">Alice Hoffman&apos;s books are always so beautiful and magical, I love reading them. They transport me to a whole different world, where I can dream and forget my day-to-day reality. <br/>These are the kind of books that make me get lost in the city, that make me ride public transports way past my exit, that make me dream while I&apos;m wide awake.<br/>I love her books, the complexity of her characters, the richness of her stories. Whenever I start one of her books, I feel myself being drawn to plot. And it is alwa</span>
  <span id="freeText4298338191782475205" style="display:none">Alice Hoffman's books are always so beautiful and magical, I love reading them. They transport me to a whole different world, where I can dream and forget my day-to-day reality. <br />These are the kind of books that make me get lost in the city, that make me ride public transports way past my exit, that make me dream while I'm wide awake.<br />I love her books, the complexity of her characters, the richness of her stories. Whenever I start one of her books, I feel myself being drawn to plot. And it is always so difficult to end her books. I don't want to leave the magic, the dreams, the feeling that there's more to this world. </span>
  <a data-text-id="4298338191782475205" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


